When Beast Claw enters, spread the Scourge, then attach Beast Claw to that token. (Create a 2/2 green Beast creature token, or sacrifice a non-Beast creature to create a 3/3 token that's a copy of it, except it's a Beast.)
Equipped creature gets +2/+2.
Equip {4}

When Whirligig Saw enters, it deals 4 damage to up to one target creature you don't control, then attach it to up to one target creature you control.
